channel.title: Error while downloading cache?
channel.description:
When I try and start my client, it says "error while downloading cache".
Now, I'm aware that this is probably because the cache is missing, or somethings wrong with it.
1- Where would I check to see if I even have the cache. 2- If I don't, should I make one? Download one? What should I do lol, this has never happened to be before.
Thank ya :d
